    <text>
        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_acawun" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>acawun</orth></form>
                <usg><lang/></usg>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>шарить</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>ferret</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>искать в темноте</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>search in the dark</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>talingi urzacawæjæ xussæn bajagurdta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>в темноте он наощупь отыскал свою постель</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>he found his bed gropingly</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MD"/><biblScope>1940 III
                            55</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Сращение преверба %iа%i- с основой *%ičav%i-(← *%ikav%i-)
                    ‘замечать’, ‘наблюдать’ и пр.; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/>
                        <w>kow</w>
                        <gloss><q>искать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>kav-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w>čə̑v-</w>
                        <gloss><q>намечать</q></gloss></mentioned> (?), <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>kav-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>kū-</w>
                        <gloss><q>глядеть</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>замечать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="cu-x-bg"><lang/>
                        <w>чую</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="cu-x-bg"
                        ><w>чути</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
                        <w>чуять</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/>
                        <w>κοέω</w>
                        <gloss><q>замечать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>caveo</w>
                        <gloss><q>остерегаться</q></gloss></mentioned>. Эта же основа с наращением
                    начального s широко представлена в германских языках: <mentioned xml:lang="ang"><lang/>
                        <w>skauwōn</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="goh"><lang/>
                        <w>scouwōn</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/>
                        <w>scauen</w>
                        <gloss><q>смотреть</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>наблюдать</q></gloss></mentioned>; ср. д. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_asxawun"/>. Ср. %ii-gawun%i(← *%ivi-käv-%i), <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_sqawyn"/> (?).</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">The fusion of the preverb %iа%i- with the stem *%ičav%i-(←
                    *%ikav%i-) ‘notice’, ‘observe’ etc.; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/>
                        <w>kow</w>
                        <gloss><q>search</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>kav-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w>čə̑v-</w>
                        <gloss><q>mark</q></gloss></mentioned> (?), <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>kav-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>kū-</w>
                        <gloss><q>glance</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>notice</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="cu-x-bg"><lang/>
                        <w>čuju</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="cu-x-bg"
                        ><w>čuti</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
                        <w>čujat'</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/>
                        <w>κοέω</w>
                        <gloss><q>mark</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>caveo</w>
                        <gloss><q>beware of</q></gloss></mentioned>. The same stem, with the
                    augmented initial %is%i, is widely represented in Germanic languages: <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ang"><lang/>
                        <w>skauwōn</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="goh"><lang/>
                        <w>scouwōn</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/>
                        <w>scauen</w>
                        <gloss><q>look</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>watch</q></gloss></mentioned>; cf. Digor <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_asxawun"/>. Cf. %ii-gawun%i(← *%ivi-käv-%i), <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_sqawyn"/> (?).</etym>
            </entry>
